high_descs: Walk over to the couch on your right.
Pick up the rightmost blue credit card off of the couch.
Turn right and walk over to the chair.
Put the credit card on the front left corner of the seat of the chair.
Turn around and walk around the couch to the small round table in the corner of the room.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the small round table.
Turn around and walk over to the wooden table, then turn left and walk around the couch back to the chair you put the credit card on.
Put the credit card on the seat of the chair to the right of the other card.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Turn right then head towards the couch then turn to face it.
Pick up the credit card behind the remote on the couch.
Turn around then head towards the chair.
Place the credit card into the chair on the left side.
Turn right then head towards the wall, turn right again then head towards the round table.
Pick up the credit card in front of the lamp on the round table.
Turn all the way around then walk towards the television, turn left then walk towards the chair.
Place the credit card into the chair next to the other one.
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards into a chair.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward a bit, turn left,go forward, turn left at the middle of the couch
Pick up the credit card on the couch
Turn right, go to the chair
Put the credit card on the chair
Turn around, go forward, turn right and go to the round coffee table
Pick up the credit card on the coffee table
Turn around, go forward, turn left and go to the chair
Put the credit card on the chair
anns.task_desc: Bring two credit cards to the chair
